name: WebDigg
tag_list: web-directory, web-statistics, web-information, website-value, website-worth, website-competition, website-safety-reports, website-information
overview: WebDigg is a service dedicated to collecting complete information about websites. Our service stores extensive data about domains, including but not restricted to: general information, primary competitors, similar resources, and Whois information. In addition to this, WebDigg obtains various statistics from well-known web information services such as Alexa.com, Compete.com, Yahoo.com, Siteadvisor, and Mywot. To retrieve the available information, you only need to provide the intended website’s URL or a related keyword. We are constantly on the lookout for new websites, and we add them to our database as soon as they are made available.If you want to know how much traffic is coming to your site, which pages are bringing the most traffic, Alexa stats, Whois information, twitter posts, Safety Report, competitors websites, where are your visitors coming from, and when is traffic coming in, you just have to analyze your websiteâ€™s statistics.
